  <div id="home-item-about">
    <p><h2>Tyler</h2></p>
    <p><i> Owner, Creative Thinker, Consultant, Marketer, Programmer, Designer </i></p>
    <p>BIO: Tyler is dedicated to a life of helping others by breaking down challenging barriers in marketing, business, and programming. After receiving a bachelors degree in Marketing from Bob Jones University in Greenville, SC, Tyler has specialized in marketing consulting with small to medium sized businesses. He is also a self-taught programmer and designer. In his spare time, he enjoys spending time with his wife and 2 young children, investing in the stock market, and playing fantasy sports. Originally from New Hampshire, he and his family now live in Annapolis, MD.</p>
